  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee or coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the coriander powder, turmeric powder, and salt, and stir well.",
    "Add the kidney beans and stir to combine with the spice mixture.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the onion salt and serve hot."
